Yolanda Ríos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yolanda_R%C3%ADos 0 Yolanda Císcar Mateu (12 December 1951 – 26 April 2012), known professionally as Yolanda Ríos, was a Venezuelan-Spanish actress best known for her appearances on the game show Un, dos, tres... responda otra vez and her theatrical performances.
